      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Thundering Voice",
        "Client": "Frost Islands Fugitive",
        "Description": "I hear roars echoing all over,\r\nno idea where they come from.\r\nI fear it might be a Tigrex!\r\nWherever I hide, the growling\r\nfollows. Please, I beg of you...\r\nHunt the source of that sound\r\nbefore it catches up with me!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Tigrex",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Voix tonitruante",
        "Client": "Fugitif de l\u0027Archipel",
        "Description": "J\u0027entends des rugissements\r\npartout, je ne sais pas\r\nd\u0027o\u00F9 ils viennent. J\u0027ai peur\r\nque ce soit un Tigrex ! Les\r\nhurlements me suivent partout.\r\nTrouve l\u0027origine de ce bruit\r\net \u00E9limine-la, je t\u0027en prie !",
